; Tutorial Script for James Conwell's Total Chaos
; I just made this to test if spellbook hiliting actually worked or not
ErasePage

SetAPen Green152
PRINT These are 
SetAPen Yellow152
SetBPen Yellow102
UNDERLINEPRINT GROUND CREATURES
;Hilite all my creatures except flying stuff IN the spellbook
;PointTo all my creatures except flying stuff IN the spellbook

Hilite all my nonflying creatures  IN the spellbook
PointTo all my nonflying creatures  IN the spellbook
ShowPage
WaitMouseOrKey

PRINT
PRINT
SetAPen Green152
PRINT These are
SetAPen Red152
SetBPen Red102
UNDERLINEPRINT FLYING CREATURES
Hilite20 all my flying stuff in the spellbook
PointTo all my flying stuff in the spellbook
